Class ExtApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • nzilbb.util.CommandLineProgram
      • nzilbb.webapp.StandAloneWebApp
        • nzilbb.ag.automation.util.AnnotatorWebApp
          • nzilbb.ag.automation.util.ExtApp
  • @ProgramDescription(value="Utility for running annotator \'ext\' web app.",
                    arguments="name.of.annotator.class.or.jar")
public class ExtApp
extends AnnotatorWebApp
    Utility for running a stand-alone webapp for Annotator extras.

    This can be run from the command like this:

    java -classpath nzilbb.ag.jar nzilbb.ag.automation.util.ExtApp myjar.jar
